<div id="settings_plugin_atcommands_dialog" data-bind="allowBindings: true">
	<h2>{{ _('Configuration') }}</h2>
	These allow you to send commands when @ commands are encountered in code, for instance move the extruder out of the way. These should be in gcode only!

	<form class="form-horizontal">
		<div class="control-group">
			<label class="control-label" for="settings-atcommands-pause">{{ _('@pause') }}</label>
			<div class="controls">
				<textarea class="input-block-level" data-bind="value: settings.plugins.atcommands.at_pause_commands" id="settings-atcommands-pause"></textarea>
			</div>
		</div>
	</form>
</div>
